description:
Watch Maralee Dawn & Friends Season 4 Episode 4 Creepy Creatures on Vision Video

The mysterious disappearance of a Creepy Creature is solved by a science teacher. These events  morph into a personal growth experience.  

Maralee Dawn & Friends takes a refreshing and imaginative approach to Bible based childrens programming.  Each episode is jam-packed with original songs.  The action is fast paced as Master Ventriloquist Maralee Dawn and her unique puppet characters engage young viewers with adventures to exotic places, encounters with unusual creatures, and creative interactive projects.  Children assimilate the values and character qualities as naturally as eating ice cream!

Producer/Host: Maralee Dawn
Director: Christopher Bessette
Editor: OMNI Productions
Puppet Characters: Butch, Suzi, Andrew the Robot, D-Duck, D-Dog, Ms. Cratchet (Schoolteacher), Grandpa (Storyteller), Tommy (International Boy), Stephen (Southern Boy), Ms. Martin (Secretary Bird)
